data.description: Large Corner Lot, three-bedroom split plan with solar panels, water purification/filtration and brand-new carpet in bedrooms. Park your boat and other toys behind 6-foot white poly vinal privacy fence and take advantage of Elgin Grove's public boat ramp. Too many upgrades to list, but important ones are: New Solar System, New Washer & Dryer, New Shed(leased) & New carpet in all bedrooms. AC installed in 2017 and landscaping has been updated with Tangerine, Grapefruit, Persian Lime and Orange trees. Furniture is also negotiable.
